    {
        "content": "<blockquote>\n<p>I think you need to assume <code>ℕ ⊨ φ</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>perhaps either approach works... I think <code>↔</code> should suffice because the claim is that the set of structures that realize φ is exactly equal to the set of structures isomorphic to ℕ</p>",
